{"tid":1067938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海外醫生免試註冊,受訪醫生反對, 個個媒體都唔同嘅","createTime":"2019-03-19T01:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T04:21:42.000Z","uid":210755,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35e8f05b1501ed34e4b3827a3006fcde4d7915e2","tid":1067938,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:37:47.000Z","msg":"【醫療爆煲】海外醫生免試註冊　醫學會調查：五成六受訪醫生反對<br />\n香港醫學會今日（18日）公布一項醫療人手問卷調查，訪問了2,981名醫生，其中2,478人認同本港有醫生短缺情況，但其中1,667人、即約五成六受訪醫生，表明反對非本地培訓醫生，來港可獲「免試註冊」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/307591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F307591&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=cf7db6bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/307591</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9成受訪醫生認為公營醫療人手短缺 反對非本地醫生免試<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/958924-香港-9成受訪醫生認為公營醫療人手短缺+反對非本地醫生免試\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F958924-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-9%E6%88%90%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA%2B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%85%8D%E8%A9%A6&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=1f8f8937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F958924-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-9%E6%88%90%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA%2B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%85%8D%E8%A9%A6&h=3b30d391\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/958924-香港-9成受訪醫生認為公營醫療人手短缺+反對非本地醫生免試</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗起哩幾張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucKdemH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucKdemH.jpg&h=492d59bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTHeJe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTHeJe3.jpg&h=ec8c2909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4PwLtp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4PwLtp.png&h=ea54a4b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16663782274e8f441a971f1ae978e1f7f1037fa7","tid":1067938,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港醫學會提出建議，若海外專科醫生於公立醫院服務三至六年，可豁免本地執業試的實習要求。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會以問卷訪問二千八百多名本地醫生，近八成同意本港醫生短缺，當中<span style=\"color: red;\">六成八的受訪者反對海外醫生免考執業試</span>。不過，有七成受訪醫生同意為通過執業試的專科醫生豁免現時半年的實習期，而五成六的受訪醫生認為，應規定海外專科醫生須在公立醫院工作三至六年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=341342&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D341342%26refer%3D&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=f33d33da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D341342%26refer%3D&h=74f4bb36\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=341342&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"9d21bfdad9ba3a6a7a95813bdd6ace68b9664705","tid":1067938,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"香港01 同香港電台嘅數據一樣, 都係講5成半左右<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448361-20190318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448361-20190318.htm&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=04a8b1be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448361-20190318.htm&h=a18103bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448361-20190318.htm</a><br />\n醫學會調查發現，逾七成半受訪者認為本港醫生短缺；約七成人認為醫生短缺是基於醫管局管理不善，近六成半人認為源於政府政策失誤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，有約<span style=\"color: red;\">五成半受訪者指出，不贊成豁免執業資格試</span>，以讓非本地培訓醫生免試在香港正式註冊執業。至於是否同意豁免已通過執業資格試的專科醫生，可免除整個實習期，調查顯示，約六成人表示同意，當中大部分人認為有關專科醫生先要在醫管局工作至少3年或上。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會本月以問卷訪問近3000名醫生及醫科學生。醫學會指，調查反映業界普遍認為非本地培訓醫生來港執業，必須考取執業試；但歡迎進一步優化專科醫生來港執業的實習期安排，以引入更多專科人才。"},{"pid":"4ab3c854322139fdd2ac97fa33b79c3f3cc99667","tid":1067938,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"而家所有傳媒都係完全唔中立㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326c2a1a6c0b7838139a2afc4139083d55b8a387","tid":1067938,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ab3c854322139fdd2ac97fa33b79c3f3cc99667","tid":1067938,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"而家所有傳媒都係完全唔中立㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"宜家好多傳媒好似求其搵個識打字 識copy 就得, 用字又經常錯 數據又無reference 又無"}]}